{
  "stem": "22883.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I had.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and apparently, this one was different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it happened a few years before, when I was still living in Warsaw and attending the Warsaw high school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My aunt asked me to go the certain place in Warsaw and find out when the bus to Lublin, to the city of Lublin, is going, the schedule all of the buses.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Apparently, this place where the buses were departing from Warsaw was in Jewish district, where-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] where-- where the Jews were living in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Apparently, before the war, we heard no such meaning like ghetto or something like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was introduced by Germans when the Germans came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we called the-- the-- the-- part of Warsaw where the Jews lived, we called it just-- just the Jewish district, but not a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So anyway, there was plaza there, and they were standing the buses, private buses, ran by Jewish people, two different location in Poland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I looked around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was no office, and we're-- I didn't know whom to ask about the schedule of the buses to Lublin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I notice a policeman standing there, ordinary Polish policeman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I came to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was dressed as a high school boy, because high school student had the uniform in Warsaw before the war.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came-- so I came to him, and-- and nicely, I ask him if he could tell me when the bus, next bus to Lublin is going away.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he looked at me, and he said, why you not to ask when the bus to Palestine going away?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was stunned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know what to answer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went away.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
